{"tid":2079960,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無澳洲巴絲聽過雪梨靈糧堂 是咪昆錢教會","createTime":"2020-06-26T06:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T23:36:52.000Z","uid":249885,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"780de23a4b78bda9aafefadfd14fea0d9624b0ba","tid":2079960,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Si0LNaQRPEA#t=47m10s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSi0LNaQRPEA%23t%3D47m10s&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Sn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=4c60c430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Si0LNaQRPEA#t=47m10s</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫人科水支持佢個末日方舟計劃<br />\n話喺澳洲搵撻地整個自給自足嘅生態圈以渡過世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有農地有學校乜乜柒柒<br />\n叫人俾十萬澳紙佢入股<br />\n我聽到就知好撚流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題有虔誠耶撚朋友好撚信<br />\n仲想滙錢俾佢 可以點用基督教角度阻止佢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef08e6e35df88168c106d2072ceacfd37798288","tid":2079960,"uid":354581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"3個銅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcde4ba633549889adc9254ef1c7d9ab36dfabf","tid"